  <entry>
    <title>C++ Sort()函数</title>
    <url>/2020/07/18/sort/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="引用"><a href="#引用" class="headerlink" title="引用"></a>引用</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#include &lt;algorithm&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="参数"><a href="#参数" class="headerlink" title="参数"></a>参数</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">void sort (RandomAccessIterator first, RandomAccessIterator last, Compare cmp);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>1）参数first：排序数组起始地址<br>2）参数last：结束地址，最后一个数据的后一位地址<br>3）参数cmp：排序方法，默认升序</p>
<a id="more"></a>
<h2 id="默认使用"><a href="#默认使用" class="headerlink" title="默认使用"></a>默认使用</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#include&lt;iostream&gt;</span><br><span class="line">#include&lt;algorithm&gt;</span><br><span class="line">using namespace std;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">int main()&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    const int n &#x3D; 5;</span><br><span class="line">    int a[n] &#x3D; &#123;5,7,13,9,1&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">    sort(a,a+n);</span><br><span class="line">    for(int i&#x3D;0;i&lt;n;i++) cout&lt;&lt;a[i]&lt;&lt;&#39; &#39;;</span><br><span class="line">    return 0;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">运行结果：1 5 7 9 13</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="降序排序"><a href="#降序排序" class="headerlink" title="降序排序"></a>降序排序</h2><p>方法1：使用标准库greater&lt;Type&gt;()，Type为数据类型</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#include&lt;iostream&gt;</span><br><span class="line">#include&lt;algorithm&gt;</span><br><span class="line">using namespace std;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">int main()&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    const int n &#x3D; 5;</span><br><span class="line">    int a[n] &#x3D; &#123;5,7,13,9,1&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">    sort(a,a+n,greater&lt;int&gt;());</span><br><span class="line">    for(int i&#x3D;0;i&lt;n;i++) cout&lt;&lt;a[i]&lt;&lt;&#39; &#39;;</span><br><span class="line">    return 0;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">运行结果：13 9 7 5 1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>方法2：自定义cmp()函数</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#include&lt;iostream&gt;</span><br><span class="line">#include&lt;algorithm&gt;</span><br><span class="line">using namespace std;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">bool cmp(int x,int y)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    return x&gt;y;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">int main()&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    const int n &#x3D; 5;</span><br><span class="line">    int a[n] &#x3D; &#123;5,7,13,9,1&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">    sort(a,a+n,cmp);</span><br><span class="line">    for(int i&#x3D;0;i&lt;n;i++) cout&lt;&lt;a[i]&lt;&lt;&#39; &#39;;</span><br><span class="line">    return 0;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">运行结果：13 9 7 5 1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="结构体-类排序"><a href="#结构体-类排序" class="headerlink" title="结构体/类排序"></a>结构体/类排序</h2><p>方法1：结构体/类内重定义&lt;</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#include&lt;iostream&gt;</span><br><span class="line">#include&lt;algorithm&gt;</span><br><span class="line">using namespace std;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">struct point</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    int x,y;</span><br><span class="line">    bool operator &lt; (const point &amp;i) const &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        return x &lt; i.x;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">int main()&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    const int n &#x3D; 5;</span><br><span class="line">    point a[n] &#x3D; &#123;&#123;1,3&#125;,&#123;2,4&#125;,&#123;5,1&#125;,&#123;8,2&#125;,&#123;3,3&#125;&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">    sort(a,a+n);</span><br><span class="line">    for(int i&#x3D;0;i&lt;n;i++) cout&lt;&lt;&#39;(&#39;&lt;&lt;a[i].x&lt;&lt;&#39;,&#39;&lt;&lt;a[i].y&lt;&lt;&#39;)&#39;&lt;&lt;&#39; &#39;;</span><br><span class="line">    return 0;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">运行结果：(1,3) (2,4) (3,3) (5,1) (8,2)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>方法2：自定义cmp()函数：<br>&emsp;1）参数类型为排序内容的数据类型<br>&emsp;2）修改为i.y&lt;j.y，即以y值为排序依据<br>&emsp;3）修改为i.x&gt;j.x，即为降序排序<br>以下实例是以结构体Point的x值作为排序依据。</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#include&lt;iostream&gt;</span><br><span class="line">#include&lt;algorithm&gt;</span><br><span class="line">using namespace std;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">struct point</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    int x,y;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">bool cmp(point i,point j)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    return i.x &lt; j.x;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">int main()&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    const int n &#x3D; 5;</span><br><span class="line">    point a[n] &#x3D; &#123;&#123;1,3&#125;,&#123;2,4&#125;,&#123;5,1&#125;,&#123;8,2&#125;,&#123;3,3&#125;&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">    sort(a,a+n,cmp);</span><br><span class="line">    for(int i&#x3D;0;i&lt;n;i++) cout&lt;&lt;&#39;(&#39;&lt;&lt;a[i].x&lt;&lt;&#39;,&#39;&lt;&lt;a[i].y&lt;&lt;&#39;)&#39;&lt;&lt;&#39; &#39;;</span><br><span class="line">    return 0;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">运行结果：(1,3) (2,4) (3,3) (5,1) (8,2)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="容器排序"><a href="#容器排序" class="headerlink" title="容器排序"></a>容器排序</h2><p>容器vector的.begin()和.end()，即为参数</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#include&lt;iostream&gt;</span><br><span class="line">#include&lt;algorithm&gt;</span><br><span class="line">#include&lt;vector&gt;</span><br><span class="line">using namespace std;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">int main()&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    const int n &#x3D; 5;</span><br><span class="line">    int a[] &#x3D; &#123;5,7,13,9,1&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">    vector&lt;int&gt; arr(a,a+n);</span><br><span class="line">    sort(arr.begin(),arr.end());</span><br><span class="line">    for(int i&#x3D;0;i&lt;n;i++) cout&lt;&lt;arr[i]&lt;&lt;&#39; &#39;;</span><br><span class="line">    return 0;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">运行结果：1 5 7 9 13</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

]]></content>
